1. Molim vas da mi pokažete *granice* ovog parka. (Please show me the *boundaries* of this park.)
2. Nismo uspeli da pređemo *granice* između dve zemlje. (We failed to cross the *borders* between two countries.)
3. Naša kuća se nalazi tik uz *granice* sa susednom parcelom. (Our house is located right next to the *border* with the neighboring plot.)
4. Vlada je odlučila da zatvori *granice* zbog pandemije. (The government decided to close the *borders* due to the pandemic.)
5. Ova tema prelazi *granice* jedne nauke i pripada i drugim oblastima. (This topic goes beyond the *boundaries* of one science and belongs to other areas as well.)
6. Sve se više ljudi bori da sačuva *granice* svoje privatnosti u digitalnom svetu. (More and more people are struggling to maintain the *limits* of their privacy in the digital world.)
7. *Granice* našeg strpljenja su već dugo pređene. (The *limits* of our patience have been crossed for a long time.)
8. Dok smo se vozili kroz pustinju, videli smo samo *granice* horizonta. (As we were driving through the desert, we could only see the *boundaries* of the horizon.)
9. Naši pregovori su došli do *granice* neuspeha. (Our negotiations have reached the *brink* of failure.)
10. Molim vas da ne pređete *granice* u mom ponašanju. (Please do not cross the *lines* in my behavior.)